.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, traveling, fishing, baking
4 different pets are kept: pony, goldfish, horse, chinchilla
1. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
2. the owner of the pony is not to the left of the owner of the goldfish##8
3. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
4. the person who's hobby is baking is not to the right of the owner of the horse##8
5. the person who's hobby is camping is the owner of the pony##1
6. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
7. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is baking##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Hobby   | fishing   | traveling         | baking   | camping    |
| Pet         | goldfish | chinchilla | horse | pony |

