.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, lemonade, hot-chocolate, coffee
There 4 different types of food: pomegranate, corn, pumpkin, papaya
1. the person drinking coffee is somewhere between the person drinking soy-milk and the person drinking lemonade##7
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the left of the person eating pumpkin##5
3. the person drinking coffee is somewhere between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person drinking soy-milk##7
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not to the left of the person eating papaya##8
5. the person eating papaya is somewhere between the person drinking lemonade and the person eating corn##7
6. the person eating corn is somewhere to the right of the person drinking coffee##5
7. the person eating corn is not to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##8
8. the person eating corn is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Beverage   | lemonade   | hot-chocolate | coffee | soy-milk    |
| Food         | pomegranate | papaya   | pumpkin   | corn |

