3. the person traveling to rome is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##5
4. the person traveling to london is not to the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##8
5. the person traveling to london is not to the left of the lawyer##8
6. the police-officer is on the left or right of the project-manager##3
7. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
8. the police-officer is on the left of the journalist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Job   | lawyer      | project-manager | police-officer | journalist   |
| City      | san-francisco | rome | london  | hannover |

