4. the entrepreneur is somewhere to the right of the owner of the pony##5
5. the owner of the turtle is the owner of the turtle##1
6. the coach is not the owner of the guinea-pig##6
7. the writer is not to the right of the coach##8
8. the owner of the pony is not to the left of the owner of the turtle##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Job   | writer   | nurse | coach | entrepreneur |
| Pet     | cat | turtle       | pony  | guinea-pig    |

