.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-12::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, amaryllis, dahlia, balloon-flower
4 different pets are kept: snake, chinchilla, rat, turtle
1. the person who growsdahlia is not to the right of the owner of the turtle##8
2. the owner of the snake is not to the right of the person who growsamaryllis##8
3. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##5
4. the owner of the snake is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who growsdahlia is between the owner of the turtle and the owner of the rat##2
6. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far left##1
7. the person who growsdahlia is on the left or right of the owner of the turtle##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Flower    | amaryllis        | balloon-flower | dahlia      | azalea    |
| Pet   | snake | rat   | chinchilla | turtle |

