.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-13::.
City: hamburg, boston, london, liverpool
There are 4 different favourite colors: purple, chestnut, black, ebony
1. the person who likes ebony is not to the right of the person who likes purple##8
2. the person who likes ebony is not to the right of the person traveling to hamburg##8
3. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
4. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who likes purple is somewhere between the person who likes black and the person traveling to boston##7
7. the person who likes purple is on the left or right of the person traveling to boston##3
8. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left or right of the person traveling to boston##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |    3     |     4      |
| City   | liverpool | boston         | london    | hamburg       |
| Color      | chestnut | ebony | purple | black |

