.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-14::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, biathlon, volleyball, snowboarding
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, aristoff, dannemann, havana
1. the havana-smoker is not to the left of the aristoff-smoker##8
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is in an odd position##4
3. the havana-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##5
4. the person who's sport is biathlon is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the dannemann-smoker##2
5. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far left##1
6. the davidoff-smoker is between the aristoff-smoker and the havana-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |     3      |      4       |
| Sport   | swimming     | biathlon | snowboarding        | volleyball       |
| Cigar      | dannemann | aristoff  | davidoff | havana |

