.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-15::.
City: marseilles, san-francisco, hamburg, new-york
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, gospel, trance, hip-hop
 1. the fan of hip-hop is somewhere to the left of the fan of trance##5
 2. the person traveling to new-york is not to the left of the person traveling to hamburg##8
 3. the person traveling to marseilles is the fan of trance##1
 4. the fan of trance is not to the right of the fan of gospel##8
 5. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 6. the fan of gospel is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to hamburg##5
 7. the fan of gospel is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person traveling to marseilles is not to the right of the fan of trance##8
 9. the fan of gospel is not to the left of the person traveling to marseilles##8
10. the person traveling to san-francisco is not to the left of the fan of country##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| City          | san-francisco    | hamburg | marseilles | new-york |
| Music-Genre   | country | hip-hop  | trance     | gospel    |

