.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, fanta, almond-milk, tea
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, bus, bike, snowmobile
1. the person driving the bus is not to the left of the person drinking fanta##8
2. the person driving the bus is not to the left of the person drinking fanta##8
3. the person driving the bike is not to the right of the person driving the bus##8
4. the person drinking almond-milk is not the person driving the snowmobile##6
5. the person drinking tea is not to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##8
6. the person driving the car is on the far right##1
7. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
8. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage           | almond-milk | tea | fanta | water   |
| Transport   | bike       | snowmobile      | bus    | car |

