2. the person drinking cola is not to the left of the person who likes blue##8
3. the person who likes blue is the person who likes blue##1
4. the person who likes purple is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
6. the person drinking mirinda is between the person who likes blue and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
7. the person drinking cola is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
