4. the australian is somewhere to the right of the person who likes brown##5
5. the australian is somewhere to the left of the russian##5
6. the french is not to the right of the australian##8
7. the person who likes coral is not to the left of the russian##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |   3   |    4    |
