.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, bongani, old-henry, siglo
4 different games are played: backgammon, mah-jongg, scrabble, whist
1. the person playing mah-jongg is not the chaman-smoker##6
2. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person playing whist##1
3. the siglo-smoker is not to the left of the person playing whist##8
4. the old-henry-smoker is the person playing backgammon##1
5. the siglo-smoker is somewhere between the person playing mah-jongg and the person playing backgammon##7
6. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
7. the person playing scrabble is between the person playing whist and the old-henry-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Cigar         | bongani    | siglo | chaman | old-henry |
| Game   | mah-jongg | whist      | scrabble     | backgammon     |

 